OL,3,CMan fined almost #3k for fly-tipping
OL,4,Ccarload of rubbish
OL,6,FA Patchway man has been ordered to pay
OL,7,F#2,950 in fines and costs after fly-
OL,8,Ftipping in South Gloucestershire.
OL,10,FHe was prosecuted by South
OL,11,FGloucestershire Council's
OL,12,Fenvironmental enforcement team after
OL,13,Fbaby clothes, garden items, and
OL,14,Fhousehold waste was discovered on
OL,15,FStation Road on February 2 last year.
OL,17,FOfficers attended the site after it
OL,18,Fwas reported to the local authority.
