OL,3,CMan fined almost #3k for fly-tipping
OL,4,Ccarload of rubbish
OL,6,FThey took photographs and seized
OL,7,Fevidence in the form of documentation
OL,8,Fwith the defendant's address on, which
OL,9,Fwas found among the waste.
OL,11,FThe man admitted responsibility for
OL,12,Fthe fly-tip when interviewed under
OL,13,Fcaution.
OL,15,FHe proceeded to Station Road the same
OL,16,Fevening after work to clear the waste
OL,17,Fhimself.
OL,19,FHe told officers he was moving and had
OL,20,Fcompletely filled his car with
OL,21,Fhousehold waste.
