OL,3,CMan fined almost #3k for fly-tipping
OL,4,Ccarload of rubbish
OL,6,FHe said he went to the local recycling
OL,7,Fcentre in Little Stoke but it was
OL,8,Fclosed when he got there, and as he
OL,9,Frequired his car for work the
OL,10,Ffollowing day, so he emptied the waste
OL,11,Finto a nearby entranceway.
OL,13,FHe added he had intended to return and
OL,14,Fdispose of the waste properly but was
OL,15,Funable to do so on the following
OL,16,FMonday or Tuesday, which is when he
OL,17,Fwas contacted by the council.
