OL,3,CMan fined almost #3k for fly-tipping
OL,4,Ccarload of rubbish
OL,6,FHe appeared at Bristol Magistrates
OL,7,FCourt on February 22, where he pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to the illegal disposal of
OL,9,Fwaste and was fined #1,996, along with
OL,10,F#773 in costs and a victim surcharge
OL,11,Fof #181.
OL,13,FCabinet Member for Communities and
OL,14,FLocal Place Cllr Rachael Hunt said:
OL,15,F"Each one of us has a responsibility
OL,16,Fto correctly dispose of our household
OL,17,Fwaste and there really is no excuse
OL,18,Ffor this type of behaviour.
