OL,3,CMan fined almost #3k for fly-tipping
OL,4,Ccarload of rubbish
OL,6,F"This gentleman should have made sure
OL,7,Fthat he was able to legally dispose of
OL,8,Fhis waste before loading his vehicle.
OL,10,F"Fly-tipping blights our countryside
OL,11,Fand has a negative impact on our
OL,12,Fcommunities and local environment.
OL,14,F"Our zero-tolerance approach to fly-
OL,15,Ftipping in South Gloucestershire means
OL,16,Fthat anyone who fly-tips here is up to
OL,17,Ffive times more likely to be
OL,18,Fprosecuted than anywhere else in the
OL,19,Fcountry."
