OL,6,FUnwanted goods and household or garden
OL,7,Fwaste can all be disposed of at no
OL,8,Fcost via the council's Sort It centres.
OL,10,FResidents who see illegal fly-tipping
OL,11,Fare encouraged to report it by using
OL,12,Fthe council's web form here or by
OL,13,Femailing streetcare@southglos.gov.uk
OL,14,For by contacting the StreetCare
OL,15,Fhelpdesk on 01454 868000.
